1201
00:41:04,128 --> 00:41:05,004
This way.

1202
00:41:05,796 --> 00:41:07,381
Ready, set, go.

1203
00:41:15,931 --> 00:41:18,017
Oh, yeah!

1204
00:41:18,100 --> 00:41:20,311
Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!

1205
00:41:20,394 --> 00:41:22,313
Yeah, come on.

1206
00:41:22,396 --> 00:41:23,272
Come on.

1207
00:41:23,856 --> 00:41:26,901
- Ooh, yes. Come on. Yes.
- Come on.

