I'll lend him to you.

1933
01:09:00,010 --> 01:09:01,679
Then Sang-soon will sleep with the guys.

1934
01:09:01,762 --> 01:09:03,597
All right, then. See you guys tomorrow.

1935
01:09:03,681 --> 01:09:04,932
- Good work today.
- Yeah.

1936
01:09:05,015 --> 01:09:06,475
- Good work today.
- Good night, <i>nuna</i>.

1937
01:09:06,559 --> 01:09:08,644
- So that's it? Nice and clean.
- Well, let's go.

1938
01:09:08,727 --> 01:09:09,979
Nice and clean, right? Namaste.

1939
01:09:10,062 --> 01:09:11,021
- Namaste.
- Namaste.

1940
01:09:11,105 --> 01:09:13,023
- <i>Shanti, shanti.</i>
- Yeah. <i>Shanti, shanti.</i>

